  "detailed_description": "<h1>Add to Wishlist</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1717787378\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1717787378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1717787378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/98c02f7f6bd25d71c260de0dc4c1e7f3.poster.avif?t=1717787378\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/98c02f7f6bd25d71c260de0dc4c1e7f3.webm?t=1717787378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/98c02f7f6bd25d71c260de0dc4c1e7f3.mp4?t=1717787378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Embark on a beautiful and minimalist journey that promises to provide a serene experience, allowing you to unwind and relax.</strong><br><br>Navigate through a <strong>myriad of colors</strong> and conquer <strong>intricate puzzle levels</strong> that progressively challenge your skills. Take control of both the white and black pieces to paint the board with amazing colors. However, be mindful as the white piece obediently follows your commands, while the black piece moves in the opposite direction simultaneously. <br><br><strong>And you cannot mix the colors!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/02abe0c2eea49f895bccc9d5a32cfadb.poster.avif?t=1717787378\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/02abe0c2eea49f895bccc9d5a32cfadb.webm?t=1717787378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/02abe0c2eea49f895bccc9d5a32cfadb.mp4?t=1717787378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Indulge in the presence of a diverse collection of a <strong>dozen exquisite koi fish</strong>, each one meticulously designed to embellish your game and create a visually captivating atmosphere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/bd4448053de53ca9d4e4c5989c8b1894.poster.avif?t=1717787378\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/bd4448053de53ca9d4e4c5989c8b1894.webm?t=1717787378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/bd4448053de53ca9d4e4c5989c8b1894.mp4?t=1717787378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Discover the perfect <strong>balance between tranquility and mental stimulation</strong> in this mesmerizing puzzle game. Can you unravel the mysteries of each level with your strategic moves?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/a397c8486d44d6dc8db9a36c1ddf8a9d.poster.avif?t=1717787378\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449680/extras/a397c8486d44d6dc8db9a36c1ddf8a9d.webm?t=1717787378\" type=\"video/webm